---
title: Creamy Roasted Veg & Prawn Curry with Naans and Soured Cream
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, this Creamy Roasted Veg & Prawn Curry combines korma curry paste and North Indian spices with prawns, roasted sweet potato and cauliflower. The creamy curry sauce is perfect for mopping up with naan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R17_W08_UK_QR3143-23_Main_low-603d131d.jpg
